        <h1 class="oe_slogan" style="font-weight: bold; text-align: center; font-size: 40px;">ADVANCE SEARCH & QUICK SEARCH</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;">From version to version, Odoo allow users to advanced search the fields by clicking the dropdown button in the header, and choosing the field along with operator & value we wish to search inside. Such method will make users takes some time and is not convenient. With the help of Advance Search & Quick Search module, users will never again encounter this kind of problem.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;">Advance Search & Quick Search allows admin to configure which fields are often search by users, and configure the most used operator from the backend side. After the configuration is done, the search features will show up above the list view and users can easily filter the datas by inputing on the columns that we have provided.</p>
